ss-date=2019-11-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191106045046/https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20191106/mobile/bkn-20191106090851403-1106_00822_001.html|archive-date=2019-11-06}}</ref>。何君堯腹部受傷，現場亦有另外兩人，包括何君堯助手受傷，全部送往[[屯門醫院|屯門醫院]]。施襲男子在現場被兩名何君堯聘請的保鑣制服，高喊「何君堯去死！何君堯揼佢！何君堯你個賊！」、「你個人渣！」。事後被警方拘捕，現場遺下懷疑是兇器的利刀<ref>{{cite news|title=【何君堯遇襲】月花逾十萬元　聘前G4貼身保護　何君堯負傷自衛|url=https://www.hk01.com/%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC/395228/%E4%BD%95%E5%90%9B%E5%A0%AF%E9%81%87%E8%A5%B2-%E6%9C%88%E8%8A%B1%E9%80%BE%E5%8D%81%E8%90%AC%E5%85%83-%E8%81%98%E5%89%8Dg4%E8%B2%BC%E8%BA%AB%E4%BF%9D%E8%AD%B7-%E4%BD%95%E5%90%9B%E5%A0%AF%E8%B2%A0%E5%82%B7%E8%87%AA%E8%A1%9B|accessdate=2019-11-07|work=香港01|date=2019-11-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191107012706/https://www.hk01.com/%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC/395228/%E4%BD%95%E5%90%9B%E5%A0%AF%E9%81%87%E8%A5%B2-%E6%9C%88%E8%8A%B1%E9%80%BE%E5%8D%81%E8%90%AC%E5%85%83-%E8%81%98%E5%89%8Dg4%E8%B2%BC%E8%BA%AB%E4%BF%9D%E8%AD%B7-%E4%BD%95%E5%90%9B%E5%A0%AF%E8%B2%A0%E5%82%B7%E8%87%AA%E8%A1%9B|archive-date=2019-11-07|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://news.tvb.com/local/5dc23033e60383ae1df66837/%E4%BD%95%E5%90%9B%E5%A0%AF%E5%B1%AF%E9%96%80%E9%81%87%E8%A5%B2%E5%8F%97%E5%82%B7%E9%80%81%E9%99%A2-%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9%E6%8B%98%E6%8D%95%E4%B8%80%E5%90%8D%E7%94%B7%E5%AD%90|title=何君堯屯門遇襲受傷送院 警方拘捕一名男子|work=無綫新聞|access-date=2019-11-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191106091842/http://news.tvb.com/local/5dc23033e60383ae1df66837/%25E4%25BD%2595%25E5%2590%259B%25E5%25A0%25AF%25E5%25B1%25AF%25E9%2596%2580%25E9%2581%2587%25E8%25A5%25B2%25E5%258F%2597%25E5%2582%25B7%25E9%2580%2581%25E9%2599%25A2-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%2596%25B9%25E6%258B%2598%25E6%258D%2595%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%2590%258D%25E7%2594%25B7%25E5%25AD%2590|archive-date=2019-11-06|dead-url=no}}</ref>。根据醫療報告，何君尧傷口位於心臟位置，闊度有2厘米，深度有2.5厘米深，亦有发炎迹象，因此医师亦有尽快进行手術的安排<ref name="hk011108">{{cite news|title=【何君堯遇襲】何君堯：已回家　感謝關心　重申要止暴制亂|url=https://www.hk01.com/%E6%94%BF%E6%83%85/396266/%E4%BD%95%E5%90%9B%E5%A0%AF%E9%81%87%E8%A5%B2-%E4%BD%95%E5%90%9B%E5%A0%AF-%E5%B7%B2%E5%9B%9E%E5%AE%B6-%E6%84%9F%E8%AC%9D%E9%97%9C%E5%BF%83-%E9%87%8D%E7%94%B3%E8%A6%81%E6%AD%A2%E6%9A%B4%E5%88%B6%E4%BA%82|accessdate=2019-11-08|work=香港01|date=2019-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191108151110/https://www.hk01.com/%E6%94%BF%E6%83%85/396266/%E4%BD%95%E5%90%9B%E5%A0%AF%E9%81%87%E8%A5%B2-%E4%BD%95%E5%90%9B%E5%A0%AF-%E5%B7%B2%E5%9B%9E%E5%AE%B6-%E6%84%9F%E8%AC%9D%E9%97%9C%E5%BF%83-%E9%87%8D%E7%94%B3%E8%A6%81%E6%AD%A2%E6%9A%B4%E5%88%B6%E4%BA%82|archive-date=2019-11-08|dead-url=no}}</ref>，并于下午完成手术。何君尧遇袭后，其亲哥也就此表示这是“意图谋杀”<ref>{{cite news|title=何君尧完成手术 其亲哥发声：这是意图谋杀|url=https://news.sina.com.cn/o/2019-11-06/doc-iicezzrr7660819.shtml|accessdate=2019-11-08|work=北京日报|date=2019-11-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191108121957/https://news.sina.com.cn/o/2019-11-06/doc-iicezzrr7660819.shtml|archive-date=2019-11-08|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

香港特区政府發言人表示，香港一向是多元、包容的社會，市民表達意見時應該和平理性，互相尊重。政府亦絕對不容忍任何暴力行為，警方會繼續嚴正執法，保障社會安寧。<ref>{{cite news|title=【何君堯遇襲】屯門擺街站遭利刀刺胸受傷　疑犯被按地制服|url=https://www.hk01.com/%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC/394982/%E4%BD%95%E5%90%9B%E5%A0%AF%E9%81%87%E8%A5%B2-%E5%B1%AF%E9%96%80%E6%93%BA%E8%A1%97%E7%AB%99%E9%81%AD%E5%88%A9%E5%88%80%E5%88%BA%E8%83%B8%E5%8F%97%E5%82%B7-%E7%96%91%E7%8A%AF%E8%A2%AB%E6%8C%89%E5%9C%B0%E5%88%B6%E6%9C%8D|accessdate=2019-11-07|work=香港01|date=2019-11-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191106025717/https://www.hk01.com/%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC/394982/%E4%BD%95%E5%90%9B%E5%A0%AF%E9%81%87%E8%A5%B2-%E5%B1%AF%E9%96%80%E6%93%BA%E8%A1%97%E7%AB%99%E9%81%AD%E5%88%A9%E5%88%80%E5%88%BA%E8%83%B8%E5%8F%97%E5%82%B7-%E7%96%91%E7%8A%AF%E8%A2%AB%E6%8C%89%E5%9C%B0%E5%88%B6%E6%9C%8D|archive-date=2019-11-06|dead-url=no}}</ref>[[国务院港澳办|国务院港澳办]]、[[香港中联办|香港中联办]]有关人士也发表声明，就此事强烈谴责<ref>{{cite news|title=国务院港澳办新闻发言人对何君尧被刺事件予以强烈谴责|url=http://www.xinhuanet.com/2019-11/08/c_1125206109.htm|accessdate=2019-11-08|work=新华网|date=2019-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191108151109/http://www.xinhuanet.com/2019-11/08/c_1125206109.htm|archive-date=2019-11-08|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=香港中联办严厉谴责凶徒蓄意刺杀何君尧议员的极端暴力犯罪行为|url=http://www.xinhuanet.com/2019-11/08/c_1125208516.htm|accessdate=2019-11-08|work=新华网|date=2019-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191108151107/http://www.xinhuanet.com/2019-11/08/c_1125208516.htm|archive-date=2019-11-08|dead-url=no}}</ref>。《[[蘋果日報_(香港)|蘋果日報]]》聲稱接獲投訴，當何君堯於屯門醫院接受治療時，原本手術輪候名單排第21位，但之後插隊至排第4，令原來輪候的病人要延遲手術。屯門醫院表示會因應病人臨床情況、手術室情況及專科人手而決定病人接受手術的先後次序。<ref>{{cite news|title=【何君堯遇襲】皮外傷享特權打尖做手術 屯院名單排21變第4|url=https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191106/60238726|accessdate=2019-11-07|work=蘋果日報|date=2019-11-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191107012652/https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191106/60238726|archive-date=2019-11-07|dead-url=no}}</ref>何君尧于8日下午出院，当时坐轮椅由其他人推出病房，并向记者舉起「OK手勢」，亦有多名警員護送，之后他在Facebook发文称已經出院回家，並表示感謝各界關心<ref name=hk011108/><ref>{{cite news|title=何君堯出院　坐輪椅由警員護送離開|url=https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1490777-20191108.htm|accessdate=2019-11-08|work=香港电台|date=2019-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191108151109/https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1490777-20191108.htm|archive-date=2019-11-08|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

